<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>信息论 on Z2X BLOG</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/tags/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA/</link><description>Recent content in 信息论 on Z2X BLOG</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.147.6</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2025 08:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.z2x-blog.top/tags/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>《信息论与编码》重点复习笔记</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9/</guid><description>《信息论与编码》重点复习笔记</description></item><item><title>九、卷积码</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/9.%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF%E7%A0%81/</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Nov 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/9.%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF%E7%A0%81/</guid><description>本节课我们系统学习了卷积码，这是通信系统中一种非常重要的差错控制编码技术。</description></item><item><title>八、循环码</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/8.%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%A0%81/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Nov 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/8.%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%A0%81/</guid><description>本节详细介绍了循环码，它是具有循环移位特性的特殊线性分组码。</description></item><item><title>七、线性分组码及其基本性质</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/7.%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E5%88%86%E7%BB%84%E7%A0%81%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/</link><pubDate>Sun, 02 Nov 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/7.%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E5%88%86%E7%BB%84%E7%A0%81%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/</guid><description>线性分组码通过引入结构化的冗余（监督位），并利用线性代数的工具，实现了一种高效、可靠的差错检测与纠正机制。</description></item><item><title>六、简单差错控制码和数学基础</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/6.%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E5%B7%AE%E9%94%99%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Fri, 31 Oct 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/6.%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E5%B7%AE%E9%94%99%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</guid><description>本章我们从工程应用的角度，深入探讨了差错控制编码的原理与方法，为后续学习更复杂的编码技术奠定了基础。</description></item><item><title>五、信道编码的基本概念</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/5.%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%93%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</link><pubDate>Fri, 31 Oct 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/5.%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%93%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</guid><description>本章我们学习了信道编码的基本理论，核心思想是通过增加冗余来对抗信道噪声，实现可靠通信。</description></item><item><title>四、率失真理论</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/4.%E7%8E%87%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Oct 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/4.%E7%8E%87%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA/</guid><description>通过学习率失真理论，我们理解了为什么MP3、JPEG等有损压缩格式是可能的，并知道了它们性能的理论上限。</description></item><item><title>三、信源编码的基本方法</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/3.%E4%BF%A1%E6%BA%90%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Sep 2025 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/3.%E4%BF%A1%E6%BA%90%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>信源编码的本质是在效率（更短的码长）和可靠性（唯一可译/低失真）之间寻找最佳平衡，而信息论为我们提供了衡量这种平衡的理论基础和实现最优编码的指导方法。</description></item><item><title>二、连续信源、信道及容量</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/2.%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E4%BF%A1%E6%BA%90/</link><pubDate>Sat, 20 Sep 2025 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/2.%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E4%BF%A1%E6%BA%90/</guid><description>通过离散化和取极限的方法，将熵的概念从离散信源推广到连续信源。</description></item><item><title>一、信息论基础</title><link>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/1.%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Sat, 06 Sep 2025 11:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.z2x-blog.top/notes/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/1.%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</guid><description>信息论是由美国科学家香农在1948年通过其论文《通信的数学理论》奠定的理论基础。</description></item></channel></rss>